{"tid":141869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"博攞諾貝爾文學獎    村上春樹新書寫「南京大屠殺死40萬人」遭日本人評擊","createTime":"2017-03-03T09:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T14:51:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70c5d016bda7b46a846f7010fb77c1f6492cbfc0","tid":141869,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170303/876791.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170303%2F876791.htm&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=eebc3420\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170303/876791.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2367/d2367907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2367%2Fd2367907.jpg&h=9f95a739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲村上春樹全新小說上架後，引發日本人批評。（圖／達志影像）<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n日本文學大師村上春樹相隔7年，在2月24日出版長篇小說《騎士団長殺し》，引發不少書迷搶購。不料村上春樹在小說中，提到「南京大屠殺」，還寫到當年大陸有40萬人被殺，讓日本網友崩潰討論，有人還發起「拒看村上春樹運動」。<br />\n<br />\n日本雅虎也報導村上春樹新書中，提到南京大屠殺的新聞，不少日本網友在下面留言討論，有日本人堅持「沒有南京大屠殺」，也有人質疑村上春樹在書中，放上南京大屠殺的內容，甚至提及死了40萬人，「他別有居心」。<br />\n<br />\n還有粉絲發起「拒看」運動，表示「身為村上的粉絲，想把這本書丟掉」，也有日本人坦言「有南京大屠殺」，但強調「當初大陸宣稱死30萬人，但村上書中引述卻說40萬人，很奇怪」。<br />\n<br />\n村上春樹在書中提及的「南京大屠殺」話題，目前他沒有對外回應，日本網友仍熱烈討論中。"},{"pid":"2ccde812c8ce87a6d4e121c578c5cc5634c982f1","tid":141869,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:37:07.000Z","msg":"日本人同支那憤青一樣on9"},{"pid":"89f67af9cd047100e5137929f815176793df8ad3","tid":141869,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"想係大陸上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c0c5720d0c99a8c9bb291623c4c0d4cca84116","tid":141869,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"大陸報細數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d3a0ffd79918359b15cd0da0e44d1398bbbbf2","tid":141869,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"有睇開村上都知道，係「發條鳥年代記」裡面有寫到二戰當時有日本軍官叫日本兵用棍打死中國人，叫士兵練習，唔好當佢係人... 轉頭由寫日本兵被蘇聯軍隊捉去勞改，監生剝皮... 村上春樹係一個極度反戰嘅作家。"},{"pid":"d0fc9e1b32f25f8eba296938c407bba02c27366b","tid":141869,"uid":50176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"反戰... 有咩問題"},{"pid":"2651bf1a08cc8c4d5ae6fc6badb6bdc0818f5199","tid":141869,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9404e057c2db9481b8de35580d7cb1fde7d3a887","tid":141869,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:49:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11dfd00bb501a14936fbbf7e9beee79c9dcd1d76","tid":141869,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"佢寫既南京大屠殺有冇話係日本人殺 ?<br />\n可能係中國人自己殺返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313a9beade67ca575802179c8e7f70d853289079","tid":141869,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:53:55.000Z","msg":"屠到三十萬呢個數擺明已經係高估左，<br />\n而家仲吹到四十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時突破五十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228d190373afe9fc3bf3084e8bf16732c4434ff8","tid":141869,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:55:16.000Z","msg":"南京有冇咁多人？"},{"pid":"5425531e25785b1bbba4243240f0dae18435081a","tid":141869,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"等睇十年後變一百萬"},{"pid":"a13fe826a7e8e5d8a0303a52fbea519b9079071e","tid":141869,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e35b8f5d231ca36c5ebd4a33c7204b96813bafd9","tid":14186